Deploying the pear2.php.net website to live
===========================================

Prerequisites
-------------
The developer needs a SSH account on `pear2.php.net` and
has to be in the `pear2web` group.


Local setup
-----------
::

$ git remote add live ssh://pear2.php.net/var/www/html/pear2.php.net


Deployment
----------
::

$ git push live master
